                                TERMS: Due on receipt <br />
                                ---------------------------------------<br />
                                ---------Tables---------------<br />
                                table 0:
                            </p>

                            <p>
                                QUANTITY, DESCRIPTION, UNIT PRICE, TOTAL <br />
                                1,12 LB Turkey,25.00,25.00<br />
                                1,1 LB Green Beans,2.50,2.50<br />
                                1,Box Stuffing,3.00,3.00<br />
                                1,10 oz Cranberry Sauce,1.50,1.50<br />
                                2,1 LB Cooked Mashed Potatoes,6.50,13.00<br />
                                2,1 Dozen Rolls,4.00,8.00<br />
                                3,Pumpkin Pie,9.50,28.50
                            </p>

                            <p>
                                table 1:<br />
